{"tid":1556930,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"義載BBC記者去機場 港版逆權司機感激報道反送中：港人永不放棄爭取自由","createTime":"2019-09-10T02:24:45.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-10T02:37:52.000Z","uid":68738,"like":30,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"a9e3ecb1d314e8e525d01c7f8562540e6340353f","tid":1556930,"uid":68738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T02:24:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190910/large/1568059073_417e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190910%2Flarge%2F1568059073_417e.jpg&h=06756167&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190910/large/1568059205_d1b4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190910%2Flarge%2F1568059205_d1b4.png&h=cfb187b0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n網民指義載情景「點解咁有畫面？好似邊套戲咁呢」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190910/large/1568059205_02d5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190910%2Flarge%2F1568059205_02d5.jpg&h=2ecce31f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n逆權司機叮囑Stephen McDonell：「唔該幫我哋話畀全世界知，香港人永遠唔會放棄！我哋會繼續爭取我哋嘅自由。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190910/large/1568059421_2d11.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190910%2Flarge%2F1568059421_2d11.jpg&h=7d08dcdb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nMcDonell採訪守護香港集會，遭大媽罵「假新聞」。(資料圖片)<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190910/large/1568059421_d712.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190910%2Flarge%2F1568059421_d712.jpg&h=31aff114&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nMcDonell手持警方發射的催淚彈和橡膠子彈，聲稱面罩被擊毀。(互聯網)<br />\n<br />\n反送中運動引發全港逾3個月的逆權運動，各行各業從業員均有人參與其中，當中除了較廣為人知的醫護界、航空界，原來連一向保守、被視為要「為口奔馳」的的士司機都支持。事緣BBC駐華記者Stephen McDonell昨天在港（9日）乘坐飛機航班離開，在搭的士去機場、到達客運大樓時，司機表示很感激國際媒體在這幾個月對反送中運動的報道，司機不僅堅持沒有收McDonell車錢，更握着McDonell的手，並叮囑他：「唔該幫我哋話畀全世界知，香港人永遠唔會放棄！我哋會繼續爭取我哋嘅自由。」<br />\n<br />\n網民隨即轉載Stephen McDonell相關tweet，並指「點解咁有畫面？好似邊套戲咁呢？香港幾時變到咁㗎？」不禁令人想起2017年上映的韓國電影《逆權司機》。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20190910/60027944?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=extra_link\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190910%2F60027944%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dextra_link&d=e21%2BqJk643s04YHbVA6HNo26uSpwD1fkwqqc2qDkc5E%3D&h=644dbc5e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190910%2F60027944%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dextra_link&h=ab48ec70\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20190910/60027944?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=extra_link</a>"},{"pid":"d3a274ea558a696e2b72fabcb0b37dcc4039ba44","tid":1556930,"uid":120431,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T02:27:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7b8b368a8a6914a8bfb9c4647d48867d7eb68a18","tid":1556930,"uid":19557,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T02:27:36.000Z","msg":"真係好似 命運一直在重復 香港人好快有民主自由 要堅持落去呀！！！！"},{"pid":"d0287cbfc8f4efd51d87e47433b150634b7df4a5","tid":1556930,"uid":68738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d3a274ea558a696e2b72fabcb0b37dcc4039ba44","tid":1556930,"uid":120431,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T02:27:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\